=== Subsidiary shrines ===
Precinct shrines are as follows<ref name="説明板"/>:
* Shirahige Shrine - deity: Sarutahiko deity
* Five-shrine group
** Yamamiya Shrine - deity: Oyamatsumi deity
** Hie Shrine - deities: Oyamakui-no-Mikoto, Hayasusanoo-no-Mikoto
** Suga Shrine - deity: Takesusanoo-no-Mikoto
** Inari Shrine - deity: Ukanomitama-no-Mikoto
** Isomae Shrine - deities: Okuninushi-no-Mikoto, Kotoshironushi-no-Mikoto
* One-shrine group

